name: Founder Membership
description:
This is the ultimate status in our **Exclusive Members Club** (EMC). It means that you are part of the **founding team** and actively participate in the direction of our projects. **Maximum supply is limited in the contract to only 300**. **This NFT** can be linked to your account on our **Starta Platform** to **unlock perks**:

## Founder Membership Advantages

- Right to vote on the board of directors of the **EMC**
- Full access to all developed / future products
- Full access to all developed / future website builders
- Exclusive Decentralized Identity on organization
- Exclusive version of the Starta Systems website and app
- Exclusive members area with extra features
- Early access to token distribution events
- Early access to all future projects
